{"tid":1549601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國歌粵語音譯","createTime":"2019-09-07T11:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T04:50:42.000Z","uid":185628,"like":72,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"8609b682122facfa66a6a22157bf9276bc8b652b","tid":1549601,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"為左方便d英文唔好既朋友參與聽日既活動<br />\n<br />\nOh, say can you see,<br />\n奥   死   驚    u     撕<br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n跛  打  當史      噓尼  厲<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed,<br />\n鑊       蘇 拋尼       v    喜 o<br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\ner 打   梯厲      屎 啦屎 劍明<br />\nWhose broad stripes and bright stars,<br />\n好屎      捕       屎摺屎  晏    跛       史打史<br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n呼            打   皮胃厲史 揮<br />\nO'er the ramparts we watched,<br />\n屙    打   ram啪       v    鑊廚<br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n華      蘇  加撚尼     史占明<br />\nAnd the rocket's red glare,<br />\n晏    打   鑊劇史   滑   茄<br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n打    泵         波士丁     煙 er<br />\nGave proof through the night,<br />\n幾乎  蒲乎   呼           打   厲此<br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n笛     R     啡    鑊    屌    爹<br />\nOh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,<br />\n奧  死   得史   笛    史打  史病高    病          夜 謂乎<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.<br />\n科   打   靚     愕乎 打 非   晏   打   空門    愕乎 打   悲乎"},{"pid":"148b39bf57f4fdb7edf5be1ed1ba61629c192cb7","tid":1549601,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a035bc0434f92a560a26acc0fff1fcaacf286cc","tid":1549601,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a21f28a2409c4f703b03