oof through the night,<br />\n幾乎 鋪 呼 打 厲<br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n笛 R 啡 鑊 屌 爹<br />\nOh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,<br />\n奧 死 得 笛 史打 病高 病喇 夜 謂乎<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.<br />\n科 打 靚 愕 打 非 晏 打 空 愕 打 悲"},{"pid":"139ed279684a4d9e715643596dac11fc66c9e792","tid":1549601,"uid":194454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:35:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">睇下呢本外國文宣啊求下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n[重開] 美國就快復會！！快啲推比外國人睇！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549540</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"530f75f6d5952c523c3f1534eb90a30b71cfb859","tid":1549601,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WS5CT04FDfU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWS5CT04FDfU&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uEzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=1c3254f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WS5CT04FDfU</a><br />\nNational Anthem of the USA - Fred Waring 1942"},{"pid":"df5567869cdf4b0d00731959f73aab72bf7bf557","tid":1549601,"uid":152171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:36:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1afba67177466eec7d77bddfa599c7c68b58ab2","tid":1549601,"uid":69707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"通勝版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cdf3b6249c59f68ef72e1e41ba6366705da3d7","tid":1549601,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b690f98608001095b71e0a74cff648ec3c8cf4","tid":1549601,"uid":109712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"畀多個意譯<br />\n<br />\nOh say can you see，by the dawn's early light<br />\n你可看見，透過一線曙光<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed，at the twilight's last gleaming？<br />\n我們對著什麼，發出歡呼的聲浪？<br />\nWhose broad stripes and bright stars，through the perilous fight<br />\n誰的寬條亮星星，在危險戰爭中<br />\nO'er the ramparts we watched，were so gallantly streaming.<br />\n依然迎風招展，在我軍碉堡上<br />\nAnd the rocket's red glare，the bombs bursting in air<br />\n火箭閃閃發光，炸彈轟轟作響<br />\nGave proof through the night，that our flag was still there<br />\n它們在黑夜中見證，國旗安然無恙<br />\nOh say does that star spangled banner yet wave<br />\n你看星條旗不是還高高飄揚<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave？<br />\n在這自由國土，勇士的家鄉？"},{"pid":"310b4a5830e278c411ea7e2b7c03f9eddb6cfc0f","tid":1549601,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:53:35.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba0ef75262a4ea7804102f97373416a8a93aeea","tid":1549601,"uid":87859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:54:47.000Z","msg":"樓主有聽民意 減屎 好野"},{"pid":"bab30b8b8572c3ee358bad25ebcc6d6613be5f18","tid":1549601,"uid":306413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:57:15.000Z","msg":"唱埋 Do you hear the people sing singing the song of angry man it is a music of a people who will not be slaves again"},{"pid":"d6a57e65a3dcc101b57167527ea635dc7f1c8d5e","tid":1549601,"uid":259674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:58:57.000Z","msg":"咪做多餘野<br />\n唔識讀就學"},{"pid":"da64f1513e58e7c0e979e8688e14eea4c1ad4ed6","tid":1549601,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:59:12.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746669e2d3396c54d50dfe8350077983d8e3c961","tid":1549601,"uid":307662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy